

Software Guidelines
===================
When you use the bugOne framework to developp apps, please to follow this 
guidelines : 

- LED1 (red one) must be used to represent the power supply. On normal 
  operation it should be ON. If your application need to power consumption,
  you can turn it OFF, but alway turn it ON when the app is running. 

- LED2 (blue one) must be used for radio channel. It should blink on receive
  or transmit. We can imagine two kind of blinking, 1 long for transmition,
  2 short blinks for reception.

- At during boot, both leds should be ON.

- Tabulation, please try to follow the GNU coding style : 4 spaces


  

